{"tid":1059550,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[狗 奴] 呢個女人可能係全世界養得最多哥基既女人","createTime":"2019-03-13T07:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T14:18:01.000Z","uid":64564,"like":737,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"0532e460b2f0a62536968091c49136ef6bfe97e6","tid":1059550,"uid":64564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.thehouseshop.com/property-blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Queens-Corgis.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehouseshop.com%2Fproperty-blog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2FQueens-Corgis.png&h=75667755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國女皇伊利莎伯二世鍾情哥基犬，自7歲開始，她就常與父親佐治六世的6隻哥基為伴，過著「公主與狗」的歡樂童年。她親自飼養過30隻哥基，英女皇雖貴為一國之君，每天親自為愛犬翻開毛髮檢查有沒有蚤子，親自餵食餵藥。在皇宮中有個Corgi Room，房間裏面每隻哥基都有一張屬於自己的私家床，冬暖夏涼，雖然狗狗最愛還是周圍瞓。聖誕節了，女皇除了為每個皇室成員預備聖誕禮物，同時也為每隻愛犬預備塞滿零食玩具的聖誕襪。做女皇的狗真幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://peopledotcom.files.wordpress.com/2018/01/queen-elizabeth-31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpeopledotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F01%2Fqueen-elizabeth-31.jpg&h=181a7001&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/queen-s-corgi/node_1718398/29339433-1-chi-HK/03_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Fqueen-s-corgi%2Fnode_1718398%2F29339433-1-chi-HK%2F03_img_885_590.jpg&h=a76e8c29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://shawglobalnews.files.wordpress.com/2018/04/gettyimages-833821520-e1524084786534.jpg?quality=70&amp;strip=all&amp;w=720&amp;h=379&amp;crop=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshawglobalnews.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F04%2Fgettyimages-833821520-e15240